
# Quick Start

0. Install [Ruby][]:
    ```sh
    brew install ruby rbenv
    eval "$(rbenv init -)"
    rbenv install 2.5.0
    rbenv local 2.5.0
    ```
0. Install [Jekyll][]: 
    ```sh
    gem install jekyll bundler
    ```
0. Install Gems from `Gemfile`:
    ```sh
    bundle install
    ```
0. Run Jekyll
    ```sh
    jekyll s
    ```
    or
    ```sh
    bundle exec jekyll s
    ```

[ruby]: https://www.ruby-lang.org/en/documentation/installation/
[jekyll]: https://jekyllrb.com/
